      teaser-event"><div class="teaser-image-container"><a href="/evenement/festival-la-rochelle-2020" target="" class="teaser-visual" title="Festival La Rochelle Cinéma 2020"><figure class="image" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject"><picture><source type="image/webp"
